Andaron Saga Official Release Date Trailer

This is the official release trailer for my upcoming Fire Emblem hack, Andaron Saga. A 31-chapter hack that aims to be as good, if not better than the mainline GBA games. The music in this trailer is composed by the musician Treatstar.

#fireemblem #romhacks #gba
